---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'top-picks', text: 'Top Picks', level: 2 },
  { id: 'how-it-works', text: 'How Telemedicine Works', level: 2 },
  { id: 'comparison-table', text: 'Plan Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'detailed-reviews', text: 'Detailed Reviews', level: 2 },
  { id: 'features', text: 'Key Features', level: 2 },
  { id: 'limitations', text: 'Limitations', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'FAQs', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Remote Worker Insurance', href: '/best/remote-worker-insurance' },
  { title: 'Digital Nomad Insurance', href: '/best/digital-nomad-insurance' },
  { title: 'Multi-Country Insurance', href: '/best/multi-country-insurance' },
  { title: 'Cigna Global Review', href: '/providers/cigna-global' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing Review', href: '/providers/safetywing' },
];

const comparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'telemedicine', header: 'Telemedicine' },
  { key: 'available', header: 'Availability' },
  { key: 'languages', header: 'Languages' },
  { key: 'cost', header: 'Additional Cost' },
];

const comparisonRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', telemedicine: 'Comprehensive', available: '24/7 worldwide', languages: 'Multiple', cost: 'Included' },
  { provider: 'Bupa Global', telemedicine: 'Comprehensive', available: '24/7 worldwide', languages: 'Multiple', cost: 'Included' },
  { provider: 'SafetyWing', telemedicine: 'Basic', available: '24/7', languages: 'English primary', cost: 'Included' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', telemedicine: 'Good', available: '24/7', languages: 'Multiple', cost: 'Included' },
  { provider: 'IMG Global', telemedicine: 'Basic', available: 'Business hours', languages: 'English', cost: 'Included' },
];

const featuresColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'premium', header: 'Premium Plans' },
  { key: 'standard', header: 'Standard Plans' },
  { key: 'travel', header: 'Travel Medical' },
];

const featuresRows = [
  { feature: 'Video consultations', premium: 'Unlimited', standard: 'Limited', travel: 'Basic' },
  { feature: 'Prescription services', premium: 'Yes + delivery', standard: 'Yes', travel: 'Limited' },
  { feature: 'Mental health', premium: 'Included', standard: 'Limited', travel: 'Usually not' },
  { feature: 'Specialist referrals', premium: 'Direct', standard: 'Coordinated', travel: 'No' },
  { feature: 'Second opinions', premium: 'Included', standard: 'Sometimes', travel: 'No' },
  { feature: 'Medical records', premium: 'Digital portal', standard: 'Varies', travel: 'No' },
  { feature: 'Languages', premium: '10+', standard: '3-5', travel: 'English' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Best Expat Insurance with Telemedicine 2026"
  description="Compare international health insurance with strong telemedicine and virtual care options. Find plans with 24/7 video doctor access worldwide."
  headline="Best Expat Insurance with Telemedicine"
  subheadline="See a doctor from anywhere in the world without leaving your home. Here are the best international health plans with comprehensive telemedicine coverage."
  heroImage="/images/answers/best-telemedicine-insurance.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  showHeroCta={false}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Plans"
  ctaButtonHref="/compare/"
>
  <h2 id="top-picks">Top Picks for Telemedicine</h2>
  <p>
    These insurers offer the best virtual healthcare options:
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">📱</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Overall Telemedicine</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Cigna Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Comprehensive telehealth with 24/7 video consultations, mental health, and prescription services worldwide.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">👑</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Premium Telemedicine</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Bupa Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Full virtual care platform with specialists, second opinions, and integrated health management.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💰</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Budget Telemedicine</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">SafetyWing</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Basic telemedicine included at $45/month. Good for simple consultations and prescriptions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🌍</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best European Telemedicine</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Allianz Care</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Strong telemedicine with excellent European language support and regional coverage.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="how-it-works">How Telemedicine Works</h2>
  <p>
    Telemedicine in international health insurance typically includes:
  </p>

  <h3>Video Consultations</h3>
  <p>
    The core telemedicine feature:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Schedule or request video calls with doctors</li>
    <li>Usually available 24/7</li>
    <li>General practitioners for most issues</li>
    <li>Some plans include specialists</li>
    <li>Works from any country with internet</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>What Telemedicine Can Handle</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Minor illnesses (cold, flu, infections)</li>
    <li>Skin conditions (with photos)</li>
    <li>Prescription refills</li>
    <li>Mental health consultations</li>
    <li>Medical advice and guidance</li>
    <li>Referrals to in-person care</li>
    <li>Second opinions on diagnoses</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>What Telemedicine Can't Handle</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Physical examinations</li>
    <li>Emergency situations</li>
    <li>Lab work and imaging</li>
    <li>Procedures and surgeries</li>
    <li>Complex diagnoses requiring in-person evaluation</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Telemedicine Options"
    description="Find plans with the virtual care features you need."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="comparison-table">Telemedicine Comparison</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={comparisonColumns} rows={comparisonRows} />
  </div>

  <h2 id="detailed-reviews">Detailed Reviews</h2>

  <h3>Cigna Global — Best Overall Telemedicine</h3>
  <p>
    Cigna Global offers one of the most comprehensive telemedicine platforms in international health insurance.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>24/7 video consultations worldwide</li>
    <li>Multiple language options</li>
    <li>Mental health via telemedicine</li>
    <li>Prescription services and delivery coordination</li>
    <li>Integrated with overall coverage</li>
    <li>Specialist consultations available</li>
    <li>Mobile app access</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Premium pricing. Best telemedicine features on higher-tier plans. Some services may vary by region.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/cigna-global">Read our full Cigna Global review</a></p>

  <h3>Bupa Global — Best Premium Telemedicine</h3>
  <p>
    Bupa Global offers a full virtual health platform with comprehensive features.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Comprehensive telehealth platform</li>
    <li>Virtual specialist consultations</li>
    <li>Second opinion services</li>
    <li>Mental health telemedicine</li>
    <li>Health coaching and wellness</li>
    <li>24/7 multilingual support</li>
    <li>Integrated health records</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Most expensive option. Full features on premium plans only. Overkill if you just need basic consultations.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/bupa-global">Read our full Bupa Global review</a></p>

  <h3>SafetyWing — Best Budget Telemedicine</h3>
  <p>
    SafetyWing includes basic telemedicine even at their low price point.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Telemedicine included at $45/month</li>
    <li>24/7 availability</li>
    <li>Good for simple consultations</li>
    <li>Can get prescriptions</li>
    <li>No appointment needed for urgent issues</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Basic features only. English-focused. No specialist consultations. Limited mental health. No prescription delivery coordination.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/safetywing">Read our full SafetyWing review</a></p>

  <h2 id="features">Key Telemedicine Features</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={featuresColumns} rows={featuresRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Mental Health Via Telemedicine</h3>
  <p>
    Mental health telemedicine is increasingly important:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Premium plans often include therapy sessions</li>
    <li>Can see psychologists/psychiatrists virtually</li>
    <li>Good for expats in areas without mental health providers</li>
    <li>Sessions in your native language</li>
    <li>Consistency regardless of location changes</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Prescription Services</h3>
  <p>
    Getting prescriptions abroad through telemedicine:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Doctor can prescribe after video consultation</li>
    <li>Prescription sent to local pharmacy</li>
    <li>Some plans coordinate international delivery</li>
    <li>Refills can be managed virtually</li>
    <li>Varies by country regulations</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Second Opinion Services</h3>
  <p>
    Premium telemedicine includes second opinions:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Submit medical records for expert review</li>
    <li>Get specialist opinion on diagnosis/treatment</li>
    <li>Valuable for serious conditions</li>
    <li>Access to specialists not available locally</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Need Virtual Care?"
    description="Compare plans with the telemedicine features that matter to you."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
  />

  <h2 id="limitations">Telemedicine Limitations</h2>

  <h3>Technical Requirements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Stable internet connection required</li>
    <li>Video calling capability (smartphone/laptop)</li>
    <li>May not work well in remote areas</li>
    <li>Time zones can affect scheduling</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Medical Limitations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>No physical examination possible</li>
    <li>Can't order tests directly (need local lab)</li>
    <li>Complex conditions need in-person care</li>
    <li>Emergency situations require local hospitals</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Regulatory Limitations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Prescriptions vary by country laws</li>
    <li>Some medications can't be prescribed remotely</li>
    <li>Controlled substances usually require in-person</li>
    <li>Some countries restrict telemedicine</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <h3>Is telemedicine included or an add-on?</h3>
  <p>
    With most international health insurers, basic telemedicine is included. Premium features (mental health, specialists, second opinions) may require higher-tier plans. Always verify what's included in your specific plan.
  </p>

  <h3>Can I get prescriptions through telemedicine abroad?</h3>
  <p>
    Usually yes, but it depends on local regulations. The telemedicine doctor can write a prescription that you take to a local pharmacy. Some insurers help coordinate delivery for ongoing medications.
  </p>

  <h3>What languages are available?</h3>
  <p>
    Premium insurers (Cigna, Bupa) offer 10+ languages. Standard plans typically offer English plus major languages. Budget options like SafetyWing are primarily English. Check your insurer's specific language offerings.
  </p>

  <h3>Can I use telemedicine for mental health?</h3>
  <p>
    Yes, with premium plans. Cigna Global and Bupa Global both offer mental health via telemedicine. Budget plans like SafetyWing have limited mental health coverage. Virtual therapy is especially valuable for expats.
  </p>

  <h3>How do video consultations work across time zones?</h3>
  <p>
    Most services are 24/7, so you can consult at any time. You may need to wait for a doctor to become available, or schedule in advance. Some services have doctors in multiple time zones.
  </p>

  <h3>Is telemedicine suitable as my only healthcare option?</h3>
  <p>
    No. Telemedicine supplements but doesn't replace in-person care. You still need access to hospitals, labs, and specialists for many conditions. Use telemedicine for convenience and minor issues.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This content is for informational purposes only. Telemedicine features vary by plan and region. We are not insurance brokers. Always verify current features directly with insurers.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
